en_404906_0	One more phase of the Lakviru meditation project, conducted by Ven Diyasenpura Wimala Thero of the Bawunseth Meditation Centre at Helummahara, Dekatana for the benefit of 60 more Army personnel including 5 Officers got underway on Friday (3).
en_404906_1	This meditation practice programme, organized by the Directorate of Psychological Operations is aimed at promoting mental well-being and stability of Army personnel.
